The theme is named Kibosh (https://github.com/tiagojsalmeida/Kibosh-Ghost-Theme).
I built myself by starting out from Casper (https://github.com/TryGhost/Casper).


My goal was to be able to add full background videos instead of images and also some customizations.
So far it's just a proof of concept and WILL NOT WORK if you use it because it's not yet public.

"If you're trying to re-build this for your own site, go ahead, but it makes the world
more boring as everything will look the same. Take shit from here and then make your
own take on it, as I think the world needs your original expression now more than anything.
YES, THE WORLD IS TOO BORING!!!111 MAKE IT EXCITING :O"
This phrase came from levels.io and truly inspires me.

-->
